==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pipeclay
<hw>Pipe"clay`</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To whiten or
clean with pipe clay, as a soldier's accouterments.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To clear off; <as>as, to <ex>pipeclay</ex>
accounts</as>.</def> <mark>[Slang, Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Piped</ent>⟦br⟧
